The Sun Revealed (TVRip)

Nature Documentary hosted by Patrick Moore, published by BBC broadcasted as part of BBC The Sky at Night series in 2008 - English narration 
http://docuwiki.net/images/5/5c/The-Sun-Revealed-TVRip-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

It's the start of a new solar cycle, as the Sun's activity is about to increase The Sky at Night looks to the Sun. The spacecraft Ulysses is coming to the end of its working life after an epic mission of 17 years observing solar activity, while the solar mission Stereo is revealing our nearest star in a new light. Plus a round-up of new developments and observations in other areas.
